OL,4,Caffected 'plume' area larger than
OL,5,Cthought
OL,7,FThe full 651-page hydrogeological
OL,8,Freport was compiled by Arcadis - a
OL,9,Fcompany which specialises in
OL,10,Fenvironmental restoration.
OL,12,FThe company visited the island on four
OL,13,Foccasions between July 2023 and May
OL,14,F2024 and tested 230 samples of water.
OL,16,FPFAS levels were checked across the St
OL,17,FOuen's Bay and Upper Pont Marquet -
OL,18,Fboth impacted areas which Jersey Water
OL,19,Fno longer draws water from.
OL,21,FWhat is PFAS?
