OL,7,FPFAS and PFOS: What is the difference?
OL,9,FPFAS contaminated several private
OL,10,Fwater supplies in the west of Jersey
OL,11,Fafter leaking from the airport in the
OL,12,F1990s, where it was being used in
OL,13,Ffirefighting foams.
OL,15,FOne of the report's key findings
OL,16,Fstates "significant PFAS
OL,17,Fcontamination" remains under the Fire
OL,18,FTraining Ground at Jersey Airport.
