OL,3,CPFAS report: 'No immediate risk' but
OL,4,Caffected 'plume' area larger than
OL,5,Cthought
OL,7,FIt recommends targeted disposal of any
OL,8,Fcontaminated soil, introducing treated
OL,9,Fwater into the supply to flush out the
OL,10,FPFAS and creating barriers to prevent
OL,11,Fits physical spread.
OL,13,FFurther testing and monitoring will
OL,14,Ftake place over the summer months to
OL,15,Fmonitor the movement of PFAS from and
OL,16,Faround the airport site.
OL,18,FThe Minister will now review the
OL,19,Freport's findings and produce a full
OL,20,Fresponse by 12 June.
